These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-9-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, blood-red, brown
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, hip-hop, techno
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, may, april
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
 1. the person drinking cola and the fan hip-hop have different parity positions##9
 2. the fan d&b is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
 3. the person drinking cola is not the person who likes blood-red##6
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 5. the fan d&b and the person who likes blood-red have different parity positions##9
 6. the fan techno is the person who likes brown##1
 7. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the fan techno##1
 9. the fan hip-hop and the person who likes brown have different parity positions##9
10. the person who's birthday is in december is the fan hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Job           | purple | blood-red | brown    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b       | hip-hop   | techno   |
| Nationality   | may    | december | april  |
| Transport     | soy-milk   | hot-chocolate       | cola |

