.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-9-2::.
3 different games are played: chess, poker, whist
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, puzzles, rock-climbing
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, february, march
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, cain, chaman
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
2. the dunhill-smoker is not to the right of the person playing chess##8
3. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
4. the person who's birthday is in july and the person playing poker have the same parity positions##9
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person playing chess have different parity positions##9
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in the middle##1
7. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3
8. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3     |
| Food          | whist  | chess         | poker |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | rock-climbing | puzzles   |
| Movie-Genre   | february     | march       | july     |
| Transport     | dunhill       | cain          | chaman    |

