.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-9-3::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, golf, skiing
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, martial-arts, zombie
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, electrician, coach
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, green, fuchsia
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##8
2. the electrician is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is golf##5
3. the person who's sport is skiing is the person who likes green##1
4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
5. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the journalist##5
6. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
7. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the left of the electrician##8
8. the person who's sport is climbing and the coach have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | climbing | golf | skiing |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie      | crime   | martial-arts  |
| Music-Genre   | coach        | journalist  | electrician         |
| Transport     | fuchsia       | aquamarine    | green       |

