3. the pall-mall-smoker and the firefighter have different parity positions##9
4. the swisher-smoker is in the middle##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
6. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##5
7. the pall-mall-smoker is in an odd position##4
8. the swisher-smoker is not to the right of the social-worker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |       3       |
