.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-9-5::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, skateboard, jet-ski
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, folk, dubstep
3 different pets are kept: ferret, hedgehog, snake
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, german, indian
1. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5
2. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the fan folk##5
3. the indian is between the fan trance and the canadian##2
4. the german is not to the right of the person driving the tram##8
5. the person driving the tram and the german have the same parity positions##9
6. the german is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##5
7. the fan folk is not to the left of the person driving the skateboard##8
8. the owner of the ferret is not to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##8
9. the owner of the snake is the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |
| Hobby         | skateboard  | jet-ski   | tram |
| Job           | folk   | dubstep | trance |
| Movie-Genre   | snake   | hedgehog  | ferret     |
| Nationality   | canadian | indian    | german  |

